overview: Aidra Fox hurt herself while biking in the mountains, somehow losing control of her bike. Lena Paul spotted her from a distance and helps Aidra by taking her home to treat her. Kenna James and Mia Malkova are at home scheming. The girls have come up with the perfect plan to make some serious coin from their sugar mama Abigail Mac. Samantha Hayes and Khloe Kapri are sitting on a bed wondering what to do with the rest of their afternoon. Khloe responds that perhaps they could have a little fun with some sensory deprivation. Meanwhile, Jenna J Ross asks Kenzie Reeves when her parents are coming back, Kenzie replies that they'll have the whole weekend to do whatever they want to each other and Kenzie comes up with a naughty, naughty idea.
title: Peer Pressure
